{"ja417:0.1":"Jataka ","ja417:0.2":"Atthakanipata ","ja417:0.3":"Kaccanivagga ","ja417:0.4":"1. Kaccanijataka ","ja417:1.1":"“Odatavattha suci allakesa, ","ja417:1.2":"Kaccani kim kumbhimadhissayitva; ","ja417:1.3":"Pittha tila dhovasi tandulani, ","ja417:1.4":"Tilodano hehiti kissahetu”. ","ja417:2.1":"“Na kho ayam brahmana bhojanattha, ","ja417:2.2":"Tilodano hehiti sadhupakko; ","ja417:2.3":"Dhammo mato tassa pahuttamajja, ","ja417:2.4":"Aham karissami susanamajjhe”. ","ja417:3.1":"“Anuvicca kaccani karohi kiccam, ","ja417:3.2":"Dhammo mato ko nu taveva samsi; ","ja417:3.3":"Sahassanetto atulanubhavo, ","ja417:3.4":"Na miyyati dhammavaro kadaci”. ","ja417:4.1":"“Dalhappamanam mama ettha brahme, ","ja417:4.2":"Dhammo mato natthi mamettha kankha; ","ja417:4.3":"Yeyeva dani papa bhavanti, ","ja417:4.4":"Te teva dani sukhita bhavanti. ","ja417:5.1":"Sunisa hi mayham vanjha ahosi, ","ja417:5.2":"Sa mam vadhitvana vijayi puttam; ","ja417:5.3":"Sa dani sabbassa kulassa issara, ","ja417:5.4":"Aham panamhi apaviddha ekika”. ","ja417:6.1":"“Jivami voham na matohamasmi, ","ja417:6.2":"Taveva atthaya idhagatosmi; ","ja417:6.3":"Ya tam vadhitvana vijayi puttam, ","ja417:6.4":"Sahava puttena karomi bhasmam”. ","ja417:7.1":"“Evanca te ruccati devaraja, ","ja417:7.2":"Mameva atthaya idhagatosi; ","ja417:7.3":"Ahanca putto sunisa ca natta, ","ja417:7.4":"Sammodamana gharamavasema”. ","ja417:8.1":"“Evanca te ruccati katiyani, ","ja417:8.2":"Hatapi santa na jahasi dhammam; ","ja417:8.3":"Tuvanca putto sunisa ca natta, ","ja417:8.4":"Sammodamana gharamavasetha. ","ja417:9.1":"Sa katiyani sunisaya saddhim, ","ja417:9.2":"Sammodamana gharamavasittha; ","ja417:9.3":"Putto ca natta ca upatthahimsu, ","ja417:9.4":"Devanamindena adhiggahita”ti. ","ja417:10.1":"Kaccanijatakam pathamam. "}